Cheltenham &amp; Gloucester is cutting its mortgage rate to 8.5 per cent
immediately for new borrowers and from December 31 for its existing
customers.
Rates at First Direct bank are reduced to 8.49 per cent from 9.25 per cent
for new borrowers and from December 21 for existing borrowers on loans which
are less than Pounds 50,000.
Chelsea building society cut rates to 8.5 per cent from 9.25 per cent for
new borrowers.
