FT  18 NOV 92 / UK Company News: BTR raises Dollars 13m from US sale
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
BTR, the industrial conglomerate, has sold US Supply, a Missouri-based
distributor of plumbing products, for Dollars 13.2m (Pounds 8.7m) cash.
The buyer was Ferguson Enterprises, the largest wholesale plumbing
distributor in the US, and a subsidiary of Wolseley, the UK building
distribution company.
BTR acquired US Supply as part of Thomas Tilling in 1983 and put it into the
Summers distribution group in 1987.
</TEXT>
